---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro'
const year = new Date().getFullYear()
---

<BaseLayout title="Privacy Policy">
  <section class="page">
    <div class="container">
      <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class="updated">Last updated: March 2026</p>

      <div class="content">
        <p>
          Milk Chug Studios ("we", "us", or "our") operates milkchugstudios.com.
          This page explains what information we collect, how we use it, and your rights
          regarding that information.
        </p>

        <h2>What We Collect</h2>
        <p>
          We do not collect any personal information such as your name, email address,
          or location. The only data we record is an anonymous play count each time a
          game is loaded on our site. This count is a simple number — it is not tied
          to any individual user or device.
        </p>

        <h2>Cookies</h2>
        <p>
          We do not use cookies or any tracking technology to identify or follow
          individual visitors across sessions or websites.
        </p>

        <h2>Third-Party Services</h2>
        <p>We use the following third-party services to operate this site:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>
            <strong>Supabase</strong> — used to store anonymous game play counts.
            Supabase may collect basic server logs as part of standard database
            operations. See their privacy policy at supabase.com/privacy.
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>Vercel</strong> — used to host and serve this website. Vercel
            may collect standard server access logs (IP address, browser type, pages
            visited) for infrastructure and security purposes. See their privacy
            policy at vercel.com/legal/privacy-policy.
          </li>
        </ul>

        <h2>Children's Privacy</h2>
        <p>
          Our site is open to all ages. We do not knowingly collect any personal
          information from anyone, including children under 13.
        </p>

        <h2>Changes to This Policy</h2>
        <p>
          We may update this privacy policy as the site grows and new features are
          added. Any changes will be reflected on this page with an updated date.
        </p>

        <h2>Contact</h2>
        <p>
          If you have any questions about this privacy policy, you can reach us at
          <strong>milkchugstudios.com</strong>.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .page {
    padding: 4rem 0;
  }

  h1 {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: -1px;
    margin-bottom: 0.4rem;
  }

  .updated {
    color: var(--muted);
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  .content {
    max-width: 640px;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1.25rem;
  }

  .content h2 {
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-top: 1rem;
  }

  .content p {
    color: var(--muted);
    line-height: 1.75;
  }

  .content ul {
    list-style: none;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.75rem;
    padding-left: 1rem;
  }

  .content ul li {
    color: var(--muted);
    line-height: 1.75;
    position: relative;
    padding-left: 1rem;
  }

  .content ul li::before {
    content: '→';
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    color: var(--accent-dark);
  }

  .content strong {
    color: var(--text);
    font-weight: 600;
  }
</style>
